oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Couple in a car
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of an unidentified man and woman sitting in a car that is stopped on a street. Handwriting at the bottom of the photograph indicates they are driving from "Memphis-Summerville [sic], Tenn." A building and other carriages can be seen behind them.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Automobiles; People; Streets
